parameters: Innkeeper: Welcome to the Golden City.
Innkeeper: What would you like to order?
Do you have any questions about the secret arena?
Clea: Do you know about the secret arena?
Innkeeper: The Pizuma Arena is located in Fotizona.

Clea: I heard that you can earn a lot of money in the secret
arena, so I thought I could get some information at the inn.

Innkeeper: This is a place for adults to socialize. Come
back when you're a little older and have some fun.
Mage Relm: P-Please don't treat me like a child!
Clea: I came up with a good idea.
Mage Relm: Sigh... It's probably something pointless, right?
Clea: Let's go on a rampage!

Mage Relm: As I thought, that's how it will be. Please be
careful... We are strong, you know!

Innkeeper: Very well, I'll forcefully make you leave the
establishment!
3ページ目にも同じ戦闘処理、戦闘後処理があるため注意すること
Innkeeper: Hey, you've come back again, huh?
Innkeeper: I'll treat you the same way as last time!
2ページ目にも同じ戦闘処理、戦闘後処理があるため注意すること

What strength... and those faces... I feel like I've seen
them somewhere before...

Fuego with the hawk eyes: My subordinates have been rude. I
am Fuego. I am known as Hawk Eyes around here.

Fuego with the hawk eyes: I've heard about your achievements
in the Pizuma Arena.

Cleric Sophia: Let's skip the troublesome negotiations. We
want to earn some funds. Is there a good place for that?

Fuego with the hawk eyes: You are not just ordinary clerics.
You are capable of much more. There is a big job that suits
you.
Fuego with the hawk eyes: Now, please follow me.
Thief Nora: W-We did it, didn't we!
Clea: Simple is the best after all.

Mage Relm: Going wild to solve things is not at all
intellectual!
Cleric Sophia: Hehe, I've only just stood at the entrance.
Clea: Yes, this is where it gets serious.
Innkeeper: Welcome to the Golden City.

Innkeeper: Are you going to challenge the Absolute Champion
again?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)

Innkeeper: I can't believe you're coming back. We're happy
about it, but are you really going to challenge again?
Clea: Is it okay if we challenge with five people this time?

Voice Priestess Phoni: N-Nice to meet you! Please take care
of us!

Innkeeper: It's fine with five people. When we challenged
with ten people in the past, it was futile.
Innkeeper: Welcome to the Golden City.
Innkeeper: That area is off-limits, please stay away!

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: It was truly impressive how you
defeated the Iron Mask. As someone who scouted you, I am
proud.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Please tell me more about the search
for people.

Clea: That matter has been resolved, so there is no longer a
need to request your assistance, Fuego-san.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: I can't guarantee that it will be a
suitable replacement, but feel free to use the underground
arena as you please.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: I have plans to give you a special
request that will make use of your skills.
Clea: Understood, thank you very much.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Please continue to survive, and if
possible, I would like to have a conversation with the
person I scouted in the past.
実績 地下闘技場の挑戦者
Innkeeper: That area is off-limits, please stay away!
Innkeeper: That area is off-limits, please stay away!
Excited Man: I saw something good today too...!

Drunk customer: Welcome to the city of desires, Dromos! It's
a special city loved by the goddess Deirea!

Innkeeper: If you have money, this town can be really
comfortable, you know.
Bartender: Please place your drink orders here.

Drunk customer: It seems like they drink some muddy water
called beer in the Valt region.

Gambler Oka: I wonder if there's anyone to play cards
with...

Rookie Gambler: Miss... would you like to play High and Low
with me?
Would you like to play High and Low?
Gambler Oku: Come to me whenever you feel like playing.

Gambler Oku: This is just a game, but if you win, maybe I'll

Gambler Oku: I had quite a good time. It helped me relax

Gambler Oku: Too bad. If you have some free time, come and
